  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK194">
<l>nayaṉcārā naṉmaiyi ṉīkkum payaṉcārāp</l>
<l> paṇpiṟcoṟ pallā rakattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The words devoid of profit or pleasure which a man speaks will, being inconsistent with virtue, remove him from goodness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
